title: Top Takeaways for Vegetable Gardeners from Last Season's Garden
itunes:title: Top Takeaways for Vegetable Gardeners from Last Season's Garden
description: Get the top takeaways from this year's vegetable garden so you can make next year's garden better and increase the harvest based on this year's experience. I walk you through my biggest takeaways, what I won't be planting again, what I'll be doing more of, and my disease prevention plan. Get links and resources at https://melissaknorris.com/225 Order your copy of The Family Garden Plan and claim bonuses at http://familygardenplan.com  to help you grow more food organically.
